hotspot -A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID = unID + 1 hotspot A/2, -B/2, 0, unID: unID = unID + 1 hotspot -A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID = unID + 1 hotspot A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID = unID + 1

del 1

material gs_frame_mat
_legSideAng = atn(gs_seat_height / 0.04) _legBackAng = acs(0.06 / (gs_seat_height - 0.06)) _legFrontAng = atn((gs_seat_height - 0.03) / 0.02)

0.06 + (gs_seat_height - 0.145) / (tan(_legBackAng) * sin(_legSideAng)) - 0.01*sin(_legBackAng), gs_seat_height - 0.08 + 0.01 * cos(_legBackAng), 12, 0.06 + (gs_seat_height - 0.145) / (tan(_legBackAng) * sin(_legSideAng)), gs_seat_height - 0.08, 912, 0, -_legBackAng, 4012,
B - 0.02 - (0.06 / sin(_legFrontAng)) - (0.08 / tan(_legFrontAng)), gs_seat_height - 0.07, 12, B - 0.02 - (0.06 / sin(_legFrontAng)) - (0.08 / tan(_legFrontAng)), gs_seat_height - 0.08, 912, 0, -_legFrontAng, 4012,
B - 0.02 - (0.06 / sin(_legFrontAng)) - (0.08 - (gs_seat_height - 0.145) / sin(_legSideAng)) / tan(_legFrontAng) + 0.01 * sin(_legFrontAng), 0.06 + 0.01 * cos(_legFrontAng), 12, B - 0.02 - (0.06 / sin(_legFrontAng)) - (0.08 - (gs_seat_height - 0.145) / sin(_legSideAng)) / tan(_legFrontAng), 0.06, 912, 0, _legFrontAng - 180, 4012
muly 1/sin(_legSideAng) rotz -90
for i = 1 to 2 rotx _legSideAng addx -B addz -0.015
cutform NSP/3, 1, 1+2, 0, 0, 0.015, 0.02,
use (NSP)
del 3
muly -1 addy -A next i
del 4 + 2
gosub "seatFrame"
cutend cutend
if not(bLegHole) then muly 1/sin(_legSideAng) rotz -90
for j = 1 to 2 rotx _legSideAng addx -B addz -0.015 cprism_ gs_frame_mat, gs_frame_mat, gs_frame_mat, NSP/3, 0.010,
use (NSP) del 3
muly -1 addy -A next j del 4 + 2
endif
for zz = 1 to NSP tempDummy = get (1) next zz

material gs_back_mat
_backHGT = ZZYZX - gs_seat_height - 0.017 _backThalRad = 0.5 * (sqr((0.11 - 0.18 * cos(30))^2 + (_backHGT - 0.08)^2)) _backAng0 = atn((0.18 * cos(30) - 0.11) / (_backHGT - 0.08)) _backAng1 = asn(0.03 / _backThalRad) - _backAng0

! --- Backrest Style 2 --- _backCurvRad = ((A/2 - 0.05)^2 + 0.0004) / 0.04 _backTopAng = asn(((A/2 - 0.05)^2 - 0.0004) / ((A/2 - 0.05)^2 + 0.0004)) _xPosCornCent = 0.05 + 0.04 * cos(_backTopAng) _yPosCornCent = _backHGT - 0.02 - 0.04 * sin(_backTopAng) _tempAngC = atn((_yPosCornCent - 0.05) / (abs(0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2) - 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)) - _xPosCornCent))) _tempAngB = acs(0.04 / sqr((_yPosCornCent - 0.05)^2 + (0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2) - 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)) - _xPosCornCent)^2)) _tempAngA = 180 - _tempAngC - _tempAngB _xPosSide = _xPosCornCent - 0.04 * cos(_tempAngA) _yPosSide = _yPosCornCent - 0.04 * sin(_tempAngA)

add A, B - 0.05, gs_seat_height + 0.017 rotx 90 roty -90
gosub "backCutpol"
addz -A prism_ 18, 5 * A, 0, -0.04, 15+64, 0, 0, 915+64, 0, -90, 4015+64, 0.06, 0, 915+64, 0, -30, 4015+64, 0.06 - 0.18 * cos(30), 0.18 * sin(30), 915+64, 0, 30 + _backAng1, 4015+64, -0.05, _backHGT, 15, (0.008 / cos(_backAng1)) - 0.05, _backHGT, 15, 0.06 - 0.18 * cos(30) + 0.088 * cos(_backAng1), 0.18 * sin(30) + 0.088 * sin(_backAng1), 15+64, 0.06 - 0.18 * cos(30), 0.18 * sin(30), 915+64, 0, -30 - _backAng1, 4015+64, 0.06, 0, 915+64, 0, 30, 4015+64, 0, 0, 915+64, 0, 90, 4015+64, B - 0.1, -0.032, 15, B - 0.1, -0.04, 15
del 1
for i = 1 to _numCuts cutend next i
! ============================================================================== end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! end ! ! ==============================================================================

addy B rotx 90 roty -90
cutpolya 13, 1, 0, -0.01, -0.01, 15, B + 0.01, -0.01, 15, B + 0.01, gs_seat_height + 0.01, 15, -0.01, gs_seat_height + 0.01, 15, -0.01, -0.01, -1,
0.06, 0.00, 15+64, 0.06, 0.06, 915+64, 0, _legBackAng-180, 4015+64, 0.06, gs_seat_height, 15, B - 0.02, gs_seat_height, 15, B, 0.03, 15, B - 0.07, 0.00, 15+64, 0.06, 0.00, -1
del 3
rotx 90 addz -B
cprism_ gs_seat_mat, gs_seat_mat, gs_seat_mat, 12, B,
0, 0, 15, 0.04 - 0.03 * (sin(_legSideAng) - tan(_legSideAng/2)), gs_seat_height - 0.03 * (1 - cos(_legSideAng)), 15+64, 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height, 1015+64, A - 0.04 - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height, 15+64, A - 0.04 + 0.03 * (sin(_legSideAng) - tan(_legSideAng/2)), gs_seat_height - 0.03 * (1 - cos(_legSideAng)), 1015+64, A, 0, 15,
A - 0.015 * sin(_legSideAng), -0.015 * cos(_legSideAng), 15, A - 0.04 + 0.015 * sin(_legSideAng) - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height - 0.015 * (1 - cos(_legSideAng)) - 0.015, 15+64, A - 0.04 - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height - 0.015, 1015+64, 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height - 0.015, 15+64, 0.04 - 0.015 * sin(_legSideAng) + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), gs_seat_height - 0.015 * (1 - cos(_legSideAng)) - 0.015, 1015+64, 0.015 * sin(_legSideAng), -0.015 * cos(_legSideAng), 15
del 2
cutend
return
! ============================================================================== "backCutpol": ! ==============================================================================
_numCuts = 0
if iBackStyle = 1 then put 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), -0.05, 13, 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), 0, 13, 0.02 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), 0, 915+64, 0, 30, 4015+64,
A/2, _yPosCurv1, 915+64, A/2, _backHGT, 3015+64, A/2, _yPosCurv1, 915+64,
A - 0.02 - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2) - 0.02 * cos(30), 0.01, 3015+64, A - 0.02 - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), 0, 915+64, 0, 30, 4015+64, A - 0.04 - 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), -0.05, 15+64,
0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2), -0.05, -1 endif
if iBackStyle = 2 then __xPos0 = 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2)
put __xPos0, -0.05, 15+64, __xPos0, 0, 15+64, __xPos0 + 0.03, 0, 915+64, __xPos0 + 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)), 0.015, 3015+64, __xPos0 + 0.03 - 0.08 * cos(30), 0.040, 915+64, __xPos0 + 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)), 0.065, 3015+64,
_xPosSide, _yPosSide, 15+64, _xPosCornCent, _yPosCornCent, 915+64, 0.05, _backHGT - 0.02, 3015+64, A/2, _backHGT - _backCurvRad, 915+64, A - 0.05, _backHGT - 0.02, 3015+64, A - _xPosCornCent, _yPosCornCent, 915+64, A - _xPosSide, _yPosSide, 3015+64,
A - __xPos0 - 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)), 0.065, 15+64, A - __xPos0 - 0.03 + 0.08 * cos(30), 0.040, 915+64, A - __xPos0 - 0.03 * (1 - cos(30)), 0.015, 3015+64, A - __xPos0 - 0.03, 0, 915+64, A - __xPos0, 0, 3015+64, A - __xPos0, -0.05, 15+64,
__xPos0, -0.05, -1 endif
if iBackStyle = 3 then __xPos0 = 0.04 + 0.03 * tan(_legSideAng/2)
put __xPos0, -0.05, 15+64, __xPos0, 0, 15+64, __xPos0 + 0.06, 0, 915+64, 0, -30, 4015+64, __xPos0 + 0.06 - 0.09 * cos(30), 0.09 * sin(30), 915+64, 0, 60, 4015+64,
_xPosCurv2, _backHGT - 0.03, 915+64, 0, -30, 4015+64, _xPosSideCurv + 0.03, _backHGT - 0.03, 915+64, 0, -90, 4015+64, A - _xPosSideCurv - 0.03, _backHGT, 15+64, A - _xPosSideCurv - 0.03, _backHGT - 0.03, 915+64, 0, -90, 4015+64, A - _xPosCurv2, _backHGT - 0.03, 915+64, 0, -30, 4015+64,
A - __xPos0 - 0.06 * (1 - cos(30)), 0.06, 15+64, A - __xPos0 - 0.06 + 0.09 * cos(30), 0.09 * sin(30), 915+64, 0, 60, 4015+64, A - __xPos0 - 0.06, 0, 915+64, 0, -30, 4015+64, A - __xPos0, 0, 15+64, A - __xPos0, -0.05, 15+64,
__xPos0, -0.05, -1 endif
roty -90
cutform NSP/3, 1, 59, 0, 0, 1, 1, get (NSP)
_numCuts = _numCuts + 1
if bBackHole and not(GLOB_CONTEXT > 20 and GLOB_CONTEXT < 30) and iBackStyle <> 3 then if iBackStyle = 1 then put 0, _yPosCurv1, 913, 0.75 * _backHGT - _yPosCurv1, 360, 4013 else put 0, _backHGT - 0.09, 913, 0.05, 360, 4013 endif
addx A/2 mulx 1 + (A/0.22 - 1) * (iBackStyle = 2) cutpolya NSP/3, 1, 0, get (NSP)

_numCuts = _numCuts + 1
endif
